data.name: AboutLog.Text
data.value:
V7 Changelog :
- Improved : Band selection now only displaying supported network band by the router. - Improved : No maximum number of bands for locking network band. - Fixed : Fixed method for POST rand GET request. This fixed session error encountered by some router model while trying to send POST ar GET request. - Fixed : Fixed repeating messagebox error while viewing 'Signal Monitoring' windows. - Added : Quick reply for messaging. - Added : Notification for new version on program startup. - Known bug : Program freeze while restarting after changing router password.
V6 Changelog :
- Compatibility : This program now works with both 32-bit and 64-bit Windows.
V5 Changelog :
- Added : Send SMS. - Added : Retrieve and view SMS. - Added : Send USSD Command.
V4 Changelog :
- Added : New Dark Theme . - Added : Signal Monitoring. Viewing the signal status from different perspective. - Removed : Basic WLAN Setting. - Fixed : Known bug for 'API Control' which GET API result displaying different output API call when the output data is empty. - Improved : Error code description will be displayed when all request (GET/POST) resulted with an error.
V3 Changelog :
- Added : View & manage connected device. - Added : Device setting. - Added : More APIs to API list. - Removed : Speedtest tool. Its broken suddenly >.<
V2 Changelog :
- Added : Reboot and shutdown option (Reported only works on certain Huawei router). - Added : Export device information. - Added : Write to API (Do at your own risk!). - Improved : Output value for Monitor Device. - Improved : Selection band option. - Improved : Speed test display a better result. - Improved : Logging output.
V1 Changelog :
- Initial release.
Note : Some features may not work on some Huawei router due to router's API won't accept request. It may be disabled by default on particular firmware for particular Huawei router.
